Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Completed in early 2021, Anode Neutral Bay is a beautifully presented, mixed-use building with only one retail premises facing Military Road.

* 45sqm* shop with 15sqm* of lower ground floor storage
* Floor to ceiling glass shopfront facing Military Road
* Excellent signage opportunities (STCA) 
* Partial fit out in place including ceiling, lighting & painted walls
* Disabled access toilet located within the tenancy
* Ducted air conditioning 
* Access to grease trap & exhaust extraction
* Surrounded by top quality retailers, gyms and medical operators, the premises would suit food & beverage, general retail, office or medical (STCA)


For further details or to arrange an inspection, please call Amy Pfeiffer 0401 198 401.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BRAND NEW RETAIL ON MILITARY ROAD

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located at the base of a new mixed-use development, with eight residential apartments and two retail shops, you can take your pick between prime Military Road exposure or a funky laneway feel.

Military Road Tenancy:

- Double storey shop totalling 121sqm*
- Floor to ceiling glass frontage
- Exclusive use stairway within tenancy plus lift access
- Adjacent to Chemist Warehouse and Vinnies and walk to Woolworths, the big four banks, Australia Post and numerous local and national retailers
- Parking directly in front plus a short walk to two Council car parks and the Woolworths car park

Could suit retail, office, hair & beauty or health/medical (STCA).

Grosvenor Lane Tenancy:

- Double storey shop totalling 110sqm*
- Floor to ceiling glass frontage
- Access to grease and exhaust
- Possibility of external seating (STCA)
- Exclusive use stairway within tenancy plus lift access
- Directly opposite Bourke Street Bakery and metres to Italian Street Kitchen, Ribs & Burgers, Grill'd, Kyushu and down from Cheese & Wine Co and The Oaks Hotel
- Surrounded by street parking and a short walk to two Council car parks and the Woolworths car park

Could suit food & beverage, retail, office, hair & beauty or health/medical (STCA).

Available now.

For further details please call Amy Pfeiffer 0401 198 401. 

*Approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: BRAND NEW RETAIL – MILITARY ROAD FRONTAGE OR LANEWAY FEEL

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Strategically located within the heart of Neutral Bay, 156 Military Road offers its Tenants pure convenience being close to Neutral Bay major bus interchange and retail strip.
 
Current Availability;

L.3 – 140 sqm- Currently fitted out as high-quality office space. Perfect for up to circa 15 staff. Fit out consists of;

• 1x boardroom
• 2 x offices or additional meeting rooms
• Large open plan area with cabled workstations
• Plumbed kitchen area + storage/ comms room


Light filled office space overlooking Military Road featuring large exclusive outdoor terrace and three underground parking spots.

For more info or to arrange a viewing time please call Tom Bennett on 0430 924 629.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Direct Pedestrian Access to Car Park
Close to Prime Retailers inc. Woolworths

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The Grove Shopping Centre - Tenanted by well-established retailers and used as a thoroughfare between Military Road, Woolworths and the Council car park, this well-known shopping precinct has only one shop remaining!

* Shop 14 – 206sqm* internally (120sqm* + 86sqm* mezzanine) + exclusive use covered balcony with abundance of natural light
* Excellent signage opportunities (STCA) facing the Council car park 
* Existing fit out in place including kitchen, bathrooms & bar area
* Connected to grease and exhaust
* Parking available if required (via separate licence).

Current retailers at The Grove include Olympus Sports, Inform Pharmacy, Iku Wholefood, Sam Thai, H & R Block plus many more.

For further details or to arrange an inspection, please contact Amy Pfeiffer 0401 198 401
